org.openimaj.util.function.context

Class ContextListTransform<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.util.function.context.ContextListTransform<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of elements in the Context being extracted
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Function<List<Context>,List<T>>

    public class ContextListTransform<T>
extends Object
implements Function<List<Context>,List<T>>
    Transform a List of Context instances to a stream of List of T. The extraction strategy is used on each item in the list.
    Author:
    Sina Samangooei (ss@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
